description_for_human: Get the historical weather for a location for a month. Make sure and pass in the month of the year the user requested. The weather temperatures will be returned in Fahrenheit. Not Found will be returned if the GPS latitude & longitude or the month of the year are not valid. Make sure and pass in valid GPS latitude & longitude for the location requested by the user. If you don't know the GPS latitude & longitude for a given location, look it up.
